                    "Cited_Guidance": "IG v3.3[7.4.2][Assumption 3][Further information about the parameters is included below in Table 1. TSVAL may have controlled terminology depending on the value of TSPARMCD]|IG v3.3[Appendix C1][If study type is INTERVENTIONAL\" this parameter is required]"
                  }
